;\"><span lang=\"AR-SA\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;\nline-height:115%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-ascii-theme-font:\nmajor-bidi;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-fareast-theme-font:\nminor-fareast;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi\">وﻛﱠﻞ\nاﻟﻤﺴﺘﺜﻤﺮُ ﺑﻤﻮﺟﺐ ﻫﺬه اﻻﺗﻔﺎﻗﻴﺔ اﻟﺸﺮﻛﺔَ ﺑﺎﺳﺘﺜﻤﺎر <a name=\"_Hlk118568324\">اﻟﻘﻴﻤﺔ\nاﻻﺳﻤﻴﺔ </a>ﻟﻠﺼﻚ</span><span dir=\"LTR\"></span><span dir=\"LTR\"></span><span dir=\"LTR\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:115%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;\nmso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\nmso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;\nmso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi\"><span dir=\"LTR\"></span><span dir=\"LTR\"></span>/</span><span lang=\"AR-SA\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:115%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;\nmso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\nmso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;\nmso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi\">اﻟﺼﻜﻮك اﻟﻤﻤﻠﻮﻛﺔ ﻟﻠﻤﺴﺘﺜﻤﺮ ﻓﻲ ﺷﺮاء <a name=\"_Hlk118568372\">ﺳﻠﻊ ﻗﺎﺑﻠﺔ ﻟﻠﺘﺴﻴﻴﻞ </a>وﺑﻴﻌﻬﺎ ﻣﺮاﺑﺤﺔ ﻟﻠﻤﺴﺘﻔﻴﺪ ﺑﺎﺳﻢ اﻟﺸﺮﻛﺔ\nوﻟﺼﺎﻟﺢ اﻟﻤﺴﺘﺜﻤﺮ وﻧﻴﺎﺑﺔً ﻋﻨﻪ، وﺑﻤﺎ ﻻ ﻳﺘﻌــﺎرض ﻣــﻊ أﺣﻜــﺎم وﻣﺒــﺎدئ اﻟﺸﺮﻳﻌــﺔ\nاﻹﺳﻼﻣﻴــﺔ، ﻛﻤــﺎ ﻳﺨــﻮل اﻟﻤﺴــﺘﺜﻤﺮُ اﻟﺸﺮﻛــﺔَ ﺑﻤﻤﺎرﺳــﺔ ﺟﻤﻴــﻊ اﻟﺤﻘــﻮق\nواﻟﺴﻠﻄﺎت واﻟﺼﻼﺣﻴﺎت اﻷﺧﺮى ذات اﻟﻌﻼﻗﺔ، واﻟﺘﻲ ﻣﻦ ﺑﻴﻨﻬﺎ ﺗﺤﺼﻴﻞ <a name=\"_Hlk118568413\">ﻣﺒﻠﻎ اﻻﺳﺘﺜﻤﺎر </a>ﻣﻦ اﻟﻤﺴﺘﻔﻴﺪ، ورﻓﻊ اﻟﺪﻋﺎوى ﻧﻴﺎﺑﺔً ﻋﻨﻪ،\nوذﻟﻚ ﻟﻴﺘﻤﻜﻦ ﻣﻦ اﻟﻮﻓﺎء ﺑﺎﻟﺘﺰاﻣﺎﺗﻪ اﻟﻨﺎﺷﺌﺔ ﺑﻤﻮﺟﺐ ﻫﺬه اﻻﺗﻔﺎﻗﻴﺔ، وﻗﺒﻞ اﻟﻄﺮف اﻷول\nذﻟﻚ</span><span dir=\"LTR\"></span><span dir=\"LTR\"></span><span dir=\"LTR\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:115%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;\nmso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\nmso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;\nmso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi\"><span dir=\"LTR\"></span><span dir=\"LTR\"></span>.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" dir=\"RTL\" style=\"margin-right: 0.5pt; direction: rtl; unicode-bidi: embed;\"><span lang=\"AR-SA\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;\nline-height:115%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-ascii-theme-font:\nmajor-bidi;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-fareast-theme-font:\nminor-fareast;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi\">اﻟﻤﺎدة\nاﻟﺜﺎﻟﺜﺔ</span><span dir=\"LTR\"></span><span dir=\"LTR\"></span><span dir=\"LTR\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:115%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;\nmso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\nmso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;\nmso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi\"><span dir=\"LTR\"></span><span dir=\"LTR\"></span>:</span><span dir=\"RTL\"></span><span dir=\"RTL\"></span><span lang=\"AR-SA\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;\nline-height:115%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-ascii-theme-font:\nmajor-bidi;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-fareast-theme-font:\nminor-fareast;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi\"><span dir=\"RTL\"></span><span dir=\"RTL\"></span> ﻃﺒﻴﻌﺔ اﻟﻨﺸﺎط اﻻﺳﺘﺜﻤﺎري وإدارﺗﻪ</span><span dir=\"LTR\"></span><span dir=\"LTR\"></span><span dir=\"LTR\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;\nline-height:115%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-ascii-theme-font:\nmajor-bidi;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-fareast-theme-font:\nminor-fareast;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi\"><span dir=\"LTR\"></span><span dir=\"LTR\"></span>:<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" dir=\"RTL\" style=\"margin-right: 0.5pt; direction: rtl; unicode-bidi: embed;\"><span dir=\"LTR\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;\nline-height:115%;font-fami